OL,3,CFirst trailer released for Amazon's
OL,4,Cdocumentary on Melania Trump
OL,6,FAmazon has revealed the first trailer
OL,7,Ffor Melania Trump's new documentary
OL,8,Ffilm, set to be released in the new
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FEntitled Melania, the film will follow
OL,12,Fthe first lady in the 20 days leading
OL,13,Fup to US President Donald Trump's
OL,14,Finauguration on January 20, 2025.
OL,16,FThe trailer opens with Mrs Trump
OL,17,Fdressed in a navy blue suit and hat as
OL,18,Fshe strolls through the US Capitol
OL,19,Frotunda ahead of her husband's second
OL,20,Finauguration.
