OL,6,F"Here we go again," she says into the
OL,7,Fcamera before showing a series of
OL,8,Fclips of her attending meetings and
OL,9,Fviewing sketches of her inauguration
OL,10,Fdress.
OL,12,FIn another moment, Melania is filmed
OL,13,Fcalling her husband after his
OL,14,Finauguration.
OL,16,F"Hi, Mr President. Congratulations,"
OL,17,Fshe says before Trump is heard asking,
OL,18,F"Did you watch it?"
OL,20,F"I did not. I will see it on the
OL,21,Fnews," she replies.
