OL,3,CFirst trailer released for Amazon's
OL,4,Cdocumentary on Melania Trump
OL,6,FAmazon Prime Video has reportedly
OL,7,Fspent $40 million (#30 million) to
OL,8,Flicense the documentary and will also
OL,9,Frelease a three-part docuseries as a
OL,10,Ffollow-up to the film.
OL,12,FIn a promotional post in October,
OL,13,FAmazon promised to provide
OL,14,F"unprecedented access" into the 20
OL,15,Fdays before the inauguration, and
OL,16,Fhopes to show "exclusive footage
OL,17,Fcapturing critical meetings, private
OL,18,Fconversations, and never-before-seen
OL,19,Fenvironments".
