OL,6,F"Everyone wants to know, so here it
OL,7,Fis," Melania says later in the trailer.
OL,9,FThe documentary was directed by Brett
OL,10,FRatner, who is known for directing the
OL,11,FRush Hour series, Red Dragon, and X-
OL,12,FMen: The Last Stand.
OL,14,FIt will mark his first film since he
OL,15,Fwas accused of sexual misconduct and
OL,16,Fharassment in 2017 during the Me Too
OL,17,Fmovement.
