OL,3,CFirst trailer released for Amazon's
OL,4,Cdocumentary on Melania Trump
OL,6,FAmazon announced in December 2024 its
OL,7,Fplans to donate $1 million (#750,000)
OL,8,Fto the President's inauguration fund
OL,9,Fand would stream the event on its
OL,10,FPrime Video service, a separate in-
OL,11,Fkind donation worth another $1 million.
OL,13,FThe documentary follows Melania's self-
OL,14,Ftitled memoir, published in 2024,
OL,15,Fwhich was later released as an
OL,16,Faudiobook narrated entirely by
OL,17,Fartificial intelligence.
OL,19,FMelania will be released in cinemas
OL,20,Fworldwide on January 30.
